Subject: P vs NP Proof-System Boundary Ledger

Description: Project-local boundary ledger for classifying proposed P vs NP coherence operators by proof-system power, certificate strength, and known lower-bound risk.

& [PvsNPProofSystemBoundaryLedger] is a math inquiry tool
  + [tool_uuid] is 1e18ee79-6de5-4d58-914c-79ac7b5af60f
  + [project] is seven math problems
  + [problem] is P versus NP
  + [created_at] is 2026-06-26T19:51Z
